high_descs: walk over to the stove tops
grab a kettle off of the stove top
bring the kettle over to the kitchen sink
clean off the kettle with water in the sink
bring the kettle back over to the stove
place the kettle on the stove
anns.task_desc: put a clean kettle on the stove

high_descs: Pick up the kettle from the stove.
Bring the kettle to the sink.
Fill the kettle with water in the sink.
Bring the filled kettle to the stove.
Put the kettle on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a filled kettle on the stove.

high_descs: Turn left, then turn right past the kitchen island, then go to the stove.
Pick up the kettle on the back, right range.
Turn around and go past the fridge, to the sink.
Wash the kettle in the sink.
Turn around and return to the stove.
Place the kettle on the front right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Wash the kettle on the stove.
